Rules for this project:

Modular Code: Always prefer splitting code into small, reusable components.

Separation of Concerns: Keep business logic (calculations, data fetching) separate from UI components. Place logic in lib/ or utils/ folders.

File Size: If a file exceeds 150 lines, suggest a way to split it into sub-components.

Consistent Style: Follow the project's existing folder structure and naming conventions.

No Spaghetti: Avoid long, nested functions. Keep the code clean and readable.